    "The sensitivity rates for the ADI, BACK, DEB, LYM, MUC, MUS, NORM, STR, and TUM classes are 99.6%, 100%, 98.8%, 99.6%, 99.8%, 99.0%, 993.%, 99.3%, and 99.0%.",
    "In contrast, in the kather_texture_2016_image_tiles dataset, the Color-CADx model establishes a sensitivity of 97.0%, 94.7%, 93.6%, 95.8%, 96.6%, 98.4%, 97.3%, and 99.5% for TUMOR, STROMA, COMPLEX, LYMPHO, DEBRIS, MUCOSA,",
