    "On the other hand, as shown in Fig. 9, the AUC for both datasets is either equal to 1 or almost 1.",
    "Experiment IV also involves the concatenation of the DCT features acquired from the three CNNs, and then applying the ANOVA FS approach to select a reduced set of features."
